trag, mkpirisi maka Entreprise Publique Economique des Tracteurs Agricoles (EPE/ETRAG/Spa), bụ ụlọ ọrụ na-ahụ maka mmepe nke igwe ọrụ ugbo
E kere ya na June 29, 2009 mgbe nkewa nke EPE CMT gasịrị.

Etrag mechiri mmekọrịta ụlọ ọrụ na azụmahịa na AGCO Massey Ferguson, onye ndu ụwa na mmepụta nke igwe ọrụ ugbo. Ha mepụtara na 16 August 2012 njikọ aka (njikọ) nke a na-akpọ Algerian Tractors Company ATC Spa
Nkwekọrịta ahụ nwere ndị mmekọ obodo abụọ ETRAG nwere (36%), Pmat na (15%) na Massey Ferguson nwere (41%)..
Kemgbe afọ 1974, e mepụtara ihe karịrị traktọ ugbo Otu narị na iri na abụọ na ụlọ ọrụ Etrag, mgbe ọ nọ n'okpuru akara Sonacome.
